description: Step into luxury with this stunning 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom condo, newly constructed in 2023 and situated in the heart of South Boston. Spanning over 1,600 square feet on a single level, this residence exudes elegance with an expansive open floor plan, drenched in natural light from over-sized windows throughout.A long foyer welcomes you into the home, setting the tone for the sophistication that follows. The gourmet kitchen is a chef’s dream, featuring custom cabinetry, top-of-the-line appliances, and  quartz counter-tops. Entertain company in the dining space that seamlessly flows into the large living space surrounded by tons of natural light. Both bedrooms are generously sized and the primary suite features a gorgeous en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub. Custom closets are integrated throughout the home, providing abundant storage space, complemented by an additional storage unit within the building. 1 garage parking space included. Furniture can be included as part of the sale.
